  dialogue:
  - 'Advisor! I have some alarming news!


    While working on the drainage project,
    our staff discovered evidence of toxic materials in a sewer down flow pipe.


    It
    seems someone has dumped these materials down there instead  of disposing of
    them.'
  - "This needs fast action Advisor.\n\nA plan of action needs your signature.\n\nSome
    ideas have already been drafted for your perusal. \n\nIf you would follow me
    please."
